<div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="display-4">Troy A. Crawford</h1>
    <p class="lead">Hello! I have built this basic log to be a centralized location to hold all of my new found knowledge. Below I break down the day's main take away. Please feel free to reach out on twitter to ask questions or leave comments. When WE all learn, WE all win!</p>
    <a href="https://troycrawford.tech" class="text-center"><h4>Portfolio: https://troycrawford.tech</h4></a>
